---
const withBase = (path: string) => {
  const base = '/arcup';
  if (path === '/') return `${base}/`;
  return `${base}${path}`;
};
---

<main id="main-content" class="page-shell page-why" aria-labelledby="why-title">
  
  <!-- HERO - Stark and Direct -->
  <header class="why-hero-v2" aria-labelledby="why-title">
    <h1 id="why-title">
      what if everyone<br />made the same choices as you?
    </h1>
    <p class="why-hero-subtitle">what world would we create?</p>
  </header>

  <!-- THE CHAT - Now the Star -->
  <section class="why-chat-v2" aria-labelledby="chat-heading">
    <!-- Chat heading moved above the window -->
    <h2 id="chat-heading" class="chat-section-heading">Conversation about innovation</h2>
    
    <div class="chat-window-v2" role="article" aria-label="Conversation about innovation patterns">
      <!-- Chat Header -->
      <header class="chat-header-v2">
        <div class="chat-avatar-v2" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div>
          <p class="chat-title-v2">#1businessBOT$$$Tips</p>
          <p class="chat-subtitle-v2">a biased conversation</p>
        </div>
      </header>

      <!-- Chat Messages -->
      <div class="chat-body-v2" id="chatBody">
        <p class="chat-timestamp-v2">SUN, 28 SEP at 22:03</p>

        <div class="chat-bubble-v2 bubble-left-v2">
          <p>what future would our choices create if we repeat the process of the past?</p>
          <span class="bubble-time">22:03</span>
        </div>

        <div class="chat-bubble-v2 bubble-right-v2">
          <p>Typically, innovation has followed wars, industrial booms-</p>
          <span class="bubble-time">22:03</span>
        </div>

        <div class="chat-bubble-v2 bubble-left-v2">
          <p>it is an old pattern</p>
          <span class="bubble-time">22:03</span>
        </div>

        <div class="chat-bubble-v2 bubble-right-v2">
          <p>a race for profit</p>
          <span class="bubble-time">22:03</span>
        </div>

        <div class="chat-bubble-v2 bubble-left-v2">
          <p>and the result ...</p>
          <span class="bubble-time">22:03</span>
        </div>

        <div class="chat-bubble-v2 bubble-right-v2">
          <p>patents? means safety! privatization? security! protection! ndas?</p>
          <span class="bubble-time">22:03</span>
        </div>

        <div class="chat-bubble-v2 bubble-left-v2">
          <p>idk</p>
          <span class="bubble-time">22:03</span>
        </div>

        <div class="chat-bubble-v2 bubble-right-v2">
          <p>money, scalability, entrepreneurs</p>
          <span class="bubble-time">22:03</span>
        </div>

        <div class="chat-bubble-v2 bubble-left-v2">
          <p>seems like concentration of power</p>
          <span class="bubble-time">22:03</span>
        </div>

        <div class="chat-bubble-v2 bubble-left-v2">
          <p>another hegemony...</p>
          <span class="bubble-time">22:03</span>
        </div>

        <div class="chat-bubble-v2 bubble-right-v2">
          <p>innovation, millionaires,</p>
          <span class="bubble-time">22:03</span>
        </div>

        <div class="chat-bubble-v2 bubble-left-v2">
          <p>at what cost tho</p>
          <span class="bubble-time">22:03</span>
        </div>

        <div class="chat-bubble-v2 bubble-right-v2">
          <p>multi-millionaires, billionaires</p>
          <span class="bubble-time">22:04</span>
        </div>

        <div class="chat-bubble-v2 bubble-left-v2">
          <p>ecocide, exploitation</p>
          <span class="bubble-time">22:04</span>
        </div>

        <div class="chat-bubble-v2 bubble-left-v2">
          <p>cultures erased, humanity lost</p>
          <span class="bubble-time">22:04</span>
        </div>

        <!-- THE PIVOT - New Ending -->
        <div class="chat-pivot">
          <div class="chat-bubble-v2 bubble-left-v2 bubble-highlight">
            <p>so what do we do differently?</p>
            <span class="bubble-time">22:05</span>
          </div>

          <div class="chat-bubble-v2 bubble-right-v2 bubble-highlight">
            <p>refuse to repeat it.</p>
            <span class="bubble-time">22:05</span>
          </div>

          <div class="chat-bubble-v2 bubble-left-v2 bubble-highlight">
            <p>how?</p>
            <span class="bubble-time">22:06</span>
          </div>

          <!-- Typing indicator -->
          <div class="chat-typing" data-typing-indicator>
            <div class="typing-bubble">
              <span class="typing-dot"></span>
              <span class="typing-dot"></span>
              <span class="typing-dot"></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="chat-status-v2">delivered</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Back to Top Button for Chat -->
    <button class="back-to-top-chat" id="backToChatTop" aria-label="Scroll to top of conversation">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
        <path d="M12 19V5M5 12l7-7 7 7"/>
      </svg>
    </button>
  </section>

  <!-- VISUAL BREAK -->
  <div class="section-divider-v2" aria-hidden="true">
    <span class="divider-label-v2">a different approach</span>
  </div>

  <!-- THE ANSWER -->
  <section class="why-answer" aria-labelledby="answer-heading">
    <header class="answer-header">
      <h2 id="answer-heading">
        arc^ refuses to copy/paste<br />the old playbook
      </h2>
    </header>

    <div class="principle-cards-v2">
      <article class="principle-card-v2">
        <h3>transparent</h3>
        <p>not hidden behind NDAs and patents</p>
      </article>

      <article class="principle-card-v2">
        <h3>collaborative</h3>
        <p>not competitive and extractive</p>
      </article>

      <article class="principle-card-v2">
        <h3>regenerative</h3>
        <p>not extractive and destructive</p>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="answer-closing">
      <p class="answer-statement">
        arc^ builds <strong>open infrastructure for collective repair</strong> â€” 
        tools, knowledge, and networks that reject the extractive paradigm.
      </p>
      <p class="answer-statement">
        Because the systems that got us here <strong>won't get us out</strong>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>

<script>
  // Back to top functionality for chat
  const chatBody = document.getElementById('chatBody');
  const backToChatTop = document.getElementById('backToChatTop');

  if (chatBody && backToChatTop) {
    chatBody.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
      if (chatBody.scrollTop > 200) {
        backToChatTop.classList.add('visible');
      } else {
        backToChatTop.classList.remove('visible');
      }
    });

    backToChatTop.addEventListener('click', () => {
      chatBody.scrollTo({
        top: 0,
        behavior: 'smooth'
      });
    });
  }
</script>